data.title: ANTHEM ~ AYN RAND ~ VINTAGE PAPERBACK ~ AUTHOR OF FOUNTAINHEAD & ATLAS SHRUGGED!
data.meta_description: Anthem has long been hailed as one of Ayn Rand's classic novels, and a clear predecessor to her later masterpieces, The Fountainhead and Atlas Shrugged. Equality 7-2521 lives in the dark ages of the future where all decisions are made by committee, all people live in collectives, and all traces of individualism have been wiped out.
